Description: OLLMchat - LLM chat application (remote backends only)
 OLLMchat is a GTK chat application with LLM access, tool integration,
 and embeddable libraries for other applications.
 .
 This all-in-one package bundles the application, shared libraries,
 GObject introspection data, and command-line tools. It is built
 without libllama: use Ollama, OpenAI-compatible HTTP APIs, and other
 remote backends only — no local GGUF inference.
 .
 For local GGUF embedding and chat via libllama, install the ollmchat
 package instead (see debian/README).
